<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/rodcet_nife.cgi?read=27" TARGET=_self>Rude Cowardly Players......</A> (Jaggr Stormaxe)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>People can be jerks sometimes but you seemed to have invited their looting spree. I trust no -ONE to loot my body, ..and if you should have to be faced with that situation again...here's what you do

<P>Set up one of your Hotkeys for the command /Corpse. Have a mage buddy of yours zip you with the Invis spells and go find your body. DO NOT loot it if there are things near, just run somewhere safe and hit the /Corpse hotkey repeatedly as you go. Then you can "drag" your body to a safe locale..
<P>Sorry to hear that you got looted, but i mightve done the same if given consent =( better luck next time..
<BR>Jack
<BR>
